1. *Kamen* je bio veoma težak. (The stone was very heavy.)
2. *Kamenje* je bilo posuto po dvorištu. (The gravel was scattered in the yard.)
3. Majstor je izrađivao skulpturu od *kamena*. (The craftsman was sculpting a stone.)
4. *Kamena* se vrata otvorila. (The stone doors opened.)
5. On je bio tvrd kao *kamen*. (He was hard as a rock.)